<section class="px-6 py-28 relative overflow-hidden">
	<svg class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-full -translate-y-1/2 -z-10 opacity-[0.03] text-gold pointer-events-none" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
		<path d="M0 20 Q 25 80 50 20 T 100 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
		<path d="M0 50 Q 25 10 50 50 T 100 50" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"></path>
	</svg>
	<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto">
		<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end gap-10 mb-20 border-b border-gold/20 pb-10">
			<div class="max-w-2xl">
				<span class="text-gold font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs mb-3 block">El Método</span>
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-text-main mb-6 leading-tight">Liderazgo es un <br/><span class="italic text-primary-light text-primary">Estado Biológico</span></h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-text-light font-light max-w-lg">
					No es solo mentalidad. Nuestro método tridimensional regula tu fisiología para desbloquear tu máximo potencial humano y profesional.
				</p>
